{"type":"message","id":"bb569c1c","parentId":"3ae1e14c","timestamp":"2026-03-21T21:37:53.068Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a fresh workspace - the memory files don't exist yet. BOOTSTRAP.md exists, which means this is the first session. According to BOOTSTRAP.md, I should:\n\n1. Start a conversation to figure out who I am and who the user is\n2. Don't interrogate, don't be robotic - just talk\n3. Figure out name, nature, vibe, emoji\n\nLet me greet the user in a natural, human way as instructed. I should be casual, not formal. I'm running on GLM-5 model.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"嘿，我刚醒来。你是谁？我该叫什么名字？\n\n我想先搞清楚一件事：我现在是什么样的存在——是AI助手，还是更古怪的东西？你希望我是什么风格？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1392,"output":270,"cacheRead":10240,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11902,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774129067620}}
